ABSTRACT:
=========
A method to minimize battery usage of a mobile device
by providing a common underlying framework for communication
of events/messages/notifications from a server to a process
that spawns the appropriate process/application that the event/
message/notification is meant for.


PURPOSE:
========
Increases battery life.

DESCRIPTION:
============


EXAMPLE:
========


AUTHOR:
=======
Anoop Kumar Narayanan
anoop at kn dot gmail at com
anoop at kumar at narayanan dot gmail at com
anoop us kn dot yahoo at com
anoop at kn dot live at in
To get the correct mail address
1. Remove spaces
2. Replace at with '.' (without single quotes)
3. Replace dot with '@' (without single quotes)
4. Replace us  with '_' (without single quotes)